<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/architects-registration-board> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Architects Registration Board (ARB) regulates the architects’ profession in the UK to ensure that good standards of conduct and practice are consistently maintained. ARB is a public corporation of the Ministry of Housing, Communities and Local Government ."@en .
